com.epoch
Class QDatum

java.lang.Object
  com.epoch.QDatum
All Implemented Interfaces:
QDatumConstants, XMLConstants
public class QDatum
extends Object
implements QDatumConstants

Data used by a question that is not associated with any one evaluator. In multiple-choice or rank questions, may be a molecule or text; in fill-blank questions, must be text; in R-group questions, must be R-group collections from which ACE chooses a shortcut group to replace each generic R group in the molecule in Figure 1. Scope: UI, Session, Data. Sessions: QSet, HWSession.
